data.description: Excellent Opportunity for the New Home phase of the ever popular Annewakee Trails Subdivision! This beautiful home is only 3 years new nestled in a cul-de-sac with a private wooded backyard. Featuring Open Floor Plan, Chef Kitchen with granite countertops, Stainless steel appliances including Highend Samsang Refridgerator! Hardwood floors thru out! Upstairs Laundry Room with new Washer/Dryer included! Private yard over looking a Nature Reserve with pond and woods. Annewakee Trail subdivision has amenities galore in sought after in Douglasville! Swim, Tennis, Playground, Splash pads, Walking Trails, and Lazy River! Everything for the whole family! Excellent Schools. Close to shopping and restaurants with easy access to the airport and downtown. ITS ALL HERE!! Attn Investors: NO RENTAL RESTRICTIONS. Great schools and excellent growing location!! Hurry! Wont Last Long!
